open questions are identified, along with the types of\nobservation that would discriminate among various models. SGRB jets may be one\nof the few observable consequences of how flows near nuclear density behave\nunder the influence of strong gravitational fields. (abridged)\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Jan 2007 20:11:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 31 Jan 2007 23:04:39 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 26 Mar 2007 18:46:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-07-19"}
