e radiation\nand from plasma-frequency emission could not be used to reproduce the observed\nfrequency dependence of the width of the average intensity profiles.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 31 Jan 2007 12:15:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
