esence of magnetic field. In addition, we\ndemonstrate that a poor signal-to-noise level in the Stokes profiles leads to a\nsignificant over-estimation of the magnetic field strength.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 31 Jan 2007 12:54:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 16 Feb 2007 13:10:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-26"}
