rom 0) which can be tuned by the external\ngate voltage; when the Rashba strength is slightly smaller than (in stead of\nequal to) the Dresselhaus strength, the diffusion length reaches its maximum;\nand then it decreases with the Rashba strength.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Jan 2007 21:38:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 2 Apr 2007 23:38:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
